{"TopicId":134396,"ForumId":36,"TopicTitle":"[1.2.1]Arkas: Development Edition","CreatedByName":"The White Guardian","CreatedById":148627,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-17T17:02:19Z","PageNum":5,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Hotdiggitydog","CreatedById":192227,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-23T15:33:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI apologize for necroing this thread, but does this still work on the newest updates? Like 1.7? I used to always play with this mod back in the day, and want to add it in, but I\u0027m afraid it might corrupt something. Thanks in advance.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JadeOfMaar","CreatedById":167617,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-25T16:00:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223588495\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022134396\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221556033623\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022192227\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Hotdiggitydog\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 4/23/2019 at 11:33 AM, Hotdiggitydog said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nbut I\u0027m afraid it might corrupt something.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMake a copy of your KSP install and strip out the weights of any unneeded mods and keep that install for testing. Throw Arkas in it and find out and share the results. I\u0027m very confident it will work just fine but the visual bundle will break. I know this from testing Arkas, Cyran and Cerillion (all of these are The White Guardian\u0027s mods) in KSP 1.4. On top of simply turning to garbage (the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Environmental Visual Enhancement (mod)\u0022\u003EEVE\u003C/abbr\u003E and scatterer effects), Scatterer 0.05x breaks configs for all versions before this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Hotdiggitydog","CreatedById":192227,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-25T19:19:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223589396\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022134396\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221556208000\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022167617\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022JadeOfMaar\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, JadeOfMaar said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMake a copy of your KSP install and strip out the weights of any unneeded mods and keep that install for testing. Throw Arkas in it and find out and share the results. I\u0027m very confident it will work just fine but the visual bundle will break. I know this from testing Arkas, Cyran and Cerillion (all of these are The White Guardian\u0027s mods) in KSP 1.4. On top of simply turning to garbage (the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Environmental Visual Enhancement (mod)\u0022\u003EEVE\u003C/abbr\u003E and scatterer effects), Scatterer 0.05x breaks configs for all versions before this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s all I need. If it doesn\u0027t work with visual mods I can\u0027t bring myself to install it. I wish this got an update, I miss it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GrandProtectorDark","CreatedById":183946,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-26T13:29:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223589486\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022134396\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221556219957\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022192227\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Hotdiggitydog\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n18 hours ago, Hotdiggitydog said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s all I need. If it doesn\u0027t work with visual mods I can\u0027t bring myself to install it. I wish this got an update, I miss it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nArkas needs a major overhaul anyway. Much of the surface is just a noisy and bumpy mess, which doesn\u0027t look like what is predented in the Lower detail scaledspace.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Hotdiggitydog","CreatedById":192227,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-26T19:28:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223589838\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022134396\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221556285357\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022183946\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022GrandProtectorDark\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, GrandProtectorDark said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nArkas needs a major overhaul anyway. Much of the surface is just a noisy and bumpy mess, which doesn\u0027t look like what is predented in the Lower detail scaledspace.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI wish, but seeing how the last update was for 1.2.1, and that The White Guardian only took it on in the absence of the OG dev, I find it unlikely it will get an update.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The White Guardian","CreatedById":148627,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-26T20:04:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223589994\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022134396\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221556306914\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022192227\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Hotdiggitydog\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n35 minutes ago, Hotdiggitydog said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI wish, but seeing how the last update was for 1.2.1, and that The White Guardian only took it on in the absence of the OG dev, I find it unlikely it will get an update.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/KPzqhEaCMgI?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Hotdiggitydog","CreatedById":192227,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-26T20:41:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTop ten anime comebacks of all time: Arkas coming back?!?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Hotdiggitydog","CreatedById":192227,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-27T14:58:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223590014\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022134396\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u