pecially one that is right before, or not far above yours...\u003Cbr\u003E\nAn @ tag for TWG would have been sufficient, rather than just hitting the *Quote* button \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E ....and I\u0027m not singling you out, I\u0027ve noticed TONS of people doing this recently... \u0026gt;:( \u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-04-27T16:26:02Z\u0022 title=\u002204/27/2019 04:26  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EApril 27, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Stone Blue\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Hotdiggitydog","CreatedById":192227,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-27T16:33:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/77721-stone-blue/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002277721\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/77721-stone-blue/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Stone Blue\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0Sorry, I\u0027m rather new to this forum, still learning. Thank you for actually being polite and helpful, unlike others on the KSP\u00A0forum that just like to put new people down.\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stone Blue","CreatedById":77721,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-27T17:07:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/192227-hotdiggitydog/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022192227\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/192227-hotdiggitydog/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Hotdiggitydog\u003C/a\u003E No problem \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nWelcome, also \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GrandProtectorDark","CreatedById":183946,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-27T19:10:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/192227-hotdiggitydog/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022192227\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/192227-hotdiggitydog/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Hotdiggitydog\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0TWG did say a bit more about his plans on the Kopernicus discord.\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\nIf you have a discord account, you may find some occasional (but still rather rare) info there.\u003Cbr\u003E\nBtw, Iirc TWG is doing a lot of work on INSTANTIATOR at the moment.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The White Guardian","CreatedById":148627,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-28T14:16:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223590252\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022134396\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221556377113\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022192227\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Hotdiggitydog\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n23 hours ago, Hotdiggitydog said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen could we see this update? Are you talkin in weeks or months?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m talking weeks. Don\u0027t worry. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/77721-stone-blue/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002277721\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/77721-stone-blue/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Stone Blue\u003C/a\u003E actually, the reasons as to why I didn\u0027t go more in-depth is because I\u0027m still not entirely certain what the update will entail. I\u0027m mostly brainstorming currently. Rest assured though that I\u0027ve gotten some ideas for breathtaking moons that I\u0027ll be creating soon, besides an overhaul for Arkas of course. Another reason for my silence is because I was en route for a week long holiday and thus had no internet access for just over a day.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLastly, a good friend of mine introduced me to a writing technique called \u0027show, don\u0027t tell\u0027, which I\u0027ll be adopting in teases going forward. As such I\u0027m not going to spill the beans on what I have planned justt, but will instead be dropping hints and pictures approaching release.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThough, as \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/183946-grandprotectordark/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022183946\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/183946-grandprotectordark/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@GrandProtectorDark\u003C/a\u003E mentioned, my primary focus is KS3P shortly followed by INSTANTIATOR. After all, primarily the latter will allow me to create some amazing new features, so it\u0027s probably best for me to finish those first so I can futher spice up any planet packs I\u0027m working on or maintaining.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stone Blue","CreatedById":77721,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-28T15:29:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/148627-the-white-guardian/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022148627\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/148627-the-white-guardian/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@The White Guardian\u003C/a\u003E Yup... I kno.. i lurk the Kop Discord as KineticSloth \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nYeah... I have since learned not finishing many projects I\u0027ve started, that \u0022show, dont tell\u0022, is prolly a good strategy \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nAnd yeah, Instantiator recently peaked my interest...\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}